    m_Alignment: 0
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "Corvin \u2014 a former court alchemist who now runs a small curiosity
    shop on the outskirts of town. He wears a worn but tidy doublet stained with
    reagents. He constantly squints due to a broken monocle and speaks quietly, as
    if sharing a secret. Under the counter, he keeps a real philosopher's stone \u2014
    except it only works during a full moon and turns metal not into gold, but into
    cheese."
